      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6812907b580a6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67f4b7e60e6e3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67b10c3e3ee93.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67b6ca5aedcd5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67c78ac8b6846.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67f46a2e503e3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67f46a2e4c154.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67f46aac1d48a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67f46b371f56b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67f46b3973067.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68119faf58da1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68128628b807c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6812862ef082f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/68965dc3e2d48.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Sword of War&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A sword by Átila Becker, inspired by the game &lt;em&gt;Darksiders&lt;/em&gt;. This was one of the original four model ZKR asked me to port, but we both forgot about it for a while. Here it is, months late.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Edit: made a few tweaks. If you already downloaded this one, please replace it with this new one.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added Sword of War at the Akkala Citadel Ruins&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/3666821"&gt;ZKR&lt;/a&gt; asked me to port some standalone items. As I finish them, I will update this page with more pictures and BNP files (since UKMM and BCML can both read them), which will be contained in a zip at some point.&lt;br&gt;Weapons will respawn with the Blood Moon.&lt;br&gt;Polinym is responsible for making a standalone of Duckboi's Long Hylian Tunic.&lt;br&gt;Madman is responsible for making a standalone of ______.&lt;br&gt;ZKR created the images of the items.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stats&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Autumn Sword&lt;br&gt;-Damage: 44&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 50&lt;br&gt;-Location: along the Death Mountain trail&lt;br&gt;Stone Sword&lt;br&gt;-Damage: 13&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 25&lt;br&gt;-Location: below Owa Daim Shrine (Stasis Trial)&lt;br&gt;Soulless Sword&lt;br&gt;-Damage: 55&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 64&lt;br&gt;-Location: Thyphlo Ruins&lt;br&gt;Death Sword&lt;br&gt;-Damage: 59&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 65&lt;br&gt;-Location: Arbiter's Grounds&lt;br&gt;Evil King's Left Blade&lt;br&gt;-Damage/Guard: 45&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 50&lt;br&gt;-Location: Gogobi Shores (east of Lurelin)&lt;br&gt;Evil King's Right Blade&lt;br&gt;-Damage: 45&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 50&lt;br&gt;-Location: Gogobi Shores (east of Lurelin)&lt;br&gt;Sword of War&lt;br&gt;-Damage: 42&lt;br&gt;-Durability: 45&lt;br&gt;-Location: Akkala Citadel Ruins&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hylian Long Tunic Set&lt;br&gt;-Defense: 3&lt;br&gt;-Location: ruins below Eastern Abbey, Aquame Lake east bank, Kolomo Garrison Ruins&lt;br&gt;Ancient Gerudo Set&lt;br&gt;-Defense: 1/3/5/7/12&lt;br&gt;-Location: Kara Kara Bazaar&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Source Links:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/550087"&gt;Autumn Sword&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://skfb.ly/oOARQ" target="_blank"&gt;Stone Sword&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://skfb.ly/6R7Aq" target="_blank"&gt;Soulless Sword&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://skfb.ly/oXOFI" target="_blank"&gt;Death Sword&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/455944"&gt;WW Ganondorf Swords&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/405717"&gt;Hylian Long Tunic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/465310"&gt;Ancient Gerudo Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
